-- Beamonte to Make Bid for Sare Holding as Soon as July 18
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   J .   L e v i n
-- 2012-07-04T19:17:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-04/beamonte-to-make-bid-for-sare-holding-as-soon-as-july-18.html
Beamonte Investments Inc. said it
plans to make a bid to buy Mexican homebuilder Sare Holding SAB
as soon as July 18, said Luis Trevino, managing director for
 Latin America  at the Boston-based private equity company.  Beamonte plans to retain an investment bank for the
transaction by tomorrow, he said today in a telephone interview
from Boston. He declined to say how much the company will pay or
the bank that will advise it on the deal.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan J. Levin at 
 jlevin20@bloomberg.net  